WEBVTT

01:40.420 --> 01:45.920
[Speed and Love]

01:46.310 --> 01:48.820
[Episode 28]

01:51.630 --> 01:53.229
Something's wrong with you.

01:54.789 --> 01:55.600
What's wrong?

01:56.070 --> 01:57.479
You're not planning...

01:58.150 --> 01:59.280
to marry Mu, are you?

02:20.440 --> 02:21.370
How did you know?

02:24.160 --> 02:26.020
Everything you bought is for her.

02:26.440 --> 02:27.570
Every single thing.

02:28.760 --> 02:29.760
And that...

02:30.480 --> 02:31.390
balut.

02:33.160 --> 02:34.420
What did you buy for me?

02:35.390 --> 02:36.040
Tell me.

02:37.950 --> 02:38.600
Eggs.

02:39.480 --> 02:40.720
For egg fried rice, see?

02:40.720 --> 02:41.520
I remembered.

02:44.920 --> 02:45.670
Let's go!

02:59.260 --> 03:01.440
♪ What would I do ♪

03:01.470 --> 03:03.940
♪ If I have 45 minutes? ♪

03:04.490 --> 03:07.200
♪ Would I write a song? ♪

03:07.680 --> 03:09.830
♪ No, I don't think so ♪

03:11.400 --> 03:13.670
♪ What would I do ♪

03:13.720 --> 03:16.079
♪ If I have 70 seconds? ♪

03:16.350 --> 03:19.079
♪ Would I get a drink or two? ♪

03:19.630 --> 03:22.090
♪ No, I don't think so ♪

03:22.910 --> 03:26.100
♪ I'd rather get on that bus ♪

03:26.630 --> 03:29.320
♪ Find you where you are ♪

03:29.790 --> 03:32.040
♪ To talk about the cloud ♪

03:32.230 --> 03:34.890
♪ That looks just like a kangaroo ♪

03:35.670 --> 03:38.640
♪ And the old man on the street ♪

03:38.980 --> 03:41.810
♪ Sat there with his dog ♪

03:42.220 --> 03:44.520
♪ Asking you if you're willing ♪

03:44.550 --> 03:47.020
♪ To accompany me too ♪

03:53.510 --> 03:54.510
Let's race.

03:56.760 --> 03:57.390
Sure.

04:02.880 --> 04:03.600
Ready.

04:03.720 --> 04:04.790
Action!

04:12.480 --> 04:13.480
Can you handle it?

04:14.000 --> 04:14.920
Beating you is not a problem.

04:14.920 --> 04:16.649
I'm only using 70% of my skills.

04:18.970 --> 04:20.500
I'll race with just one arm.

04:24.840 --> 04:26.440
You're driving really well.

04:27.350 --> 04:29.550
So about you coming back to drive for me,

04:29.720 --> 04:31.120
have you thought it over?

04:37.190 --> 04:38.450
Just drive carefully.

04:41.140 --> 04:42.500
You're my advisor.

04:43.040 --> 04:44.210
But I'd rather

04:44.240 --> 04:45.640
you come back to drive.

04:45.870 --> 04:48.130
The racing team has been waiting for you.

04:54.550 --> 04:55.159
Mu,

04:55.550 --> 04:57.150
get me a glass of water, okay?

05:07.430 --> 05:08.310
You know...

05:10.550 --> 05:11.670
why I don't drive.

05:13.790 --> 05:15.650
Let's not talk about this for now.

05:19.610 --> 05:21.760
You're a man in love now.

05:23.750 --> 05:24.550
Six years—

05:26.720 --> 05:28.780
she's been waiting for you all along.

05:29.310 --> 05:31.920
That kind of girl is truly rare.

05:32.990 --> 05:34.650
And you're not young anymore.

05:34.790 --> 05:36.520
It's normal to want stability.

05:36.720 --> 05:38.980
But you should also consider what I said.

05:49.950 --> 05:50.810
She's worth it.

06:00.520 --> 06:01.230
I won.

06:20.720 --> 06:21.400
Zhao.

06:26.040 --> 06:27.480
Zhao, Zhao, Zhao.

06:28.080 --> 06:30.210
I can't have breakfast with you today.

06:30.280 --> 06:30.920
What's wrong?

06:30.920 --> 06:31.620
I have a meeting today.

06:31.620 --> 06:33.820
I'm the first speaker. There's no time.

06:36.470 --> 06:37.490
I'm coming right now.

06:37.490 --> 06:39.090
There's no time. I have to go.

06:41.720 --> 06:43.180
I packed it. Eat on the way.

06:43.770 --> 06:46.260
Thank you. You're so thoughtful.

06:48.550 --> 06:49.230
Be careful.

06:49.870 --> 06:50.480
I'm off.

07:39.670 --> 07:42.790
Sorry, the subscriber you dialed
is busy now.

07:42.930 --> 07:44.400
Please try again later.

07:50.440 --> 07:52.500
Sorry, the subscriber you dialed...

08:32.120 --> 08:33.159
[Mu]

08:48.020 --> 08:49.310
Do you smell something?

08:49.310 --> 08:49.850
Do you smell it?

08:49.850 --> 08:50.600
Yes.

08:50.850 --> 08:51.910
What's that smell?

08:52.310 --> 08:53.190
I don't know.

08:53.790 --> 08:54.470
Wake up.

09:00.880 --> 09:01.880
Sir, the bus...

09:02.040 --> 09:03.500
-Sir!
-The bus is smoking!

09:03.710 --> 09:04.430
Sir, the bus is smoking!

09:04.430 --> 09:05.000
No way.

09:05.000 --> 09:05.950
Sir! Stop the bus! Sir!

09:05.950 --> 09:07.380
-Stop the bus!
-The bus is smoking!

09:07.380 --> 09:09.440
Okay, okay. I'm stopping right away.

09:31.970 --> 09:32.700
Mu.

09:34.880 --> 09:35.470
Zhao.

09:36.140 --> 09:36.950
Where are you?

09:38.020 --> 09:39.350
You didn't get on the bus?

09:39.350 --> 09:40.920
I'm at the convenience store downstairs.

09:40.920 --> 09:42.070
Can you bring me the documents

09:42.070 --> 09:43.040
on the table?

09:46.280 --> 09:47.000
Zhao,

09:47.470 --> 09:48.400
did you hear me?

09:52.590 --> 09:53.310
Wait for me.

10:33.690 --> 10:35.150
I'm glad that you're okay.

10:38.020 --> 10:38.690
Did you...

10:39.640 --> 10:41.210
drive here yourself?

10:52.630 --> 10:53.760
You can drive again?

11:22.190 --> 11:23.240
Slow down.

11:24.160 --> 11:25.670
Ease off the pedal suddenly.

11:25.670 --> 11:26.670
Slow down.

11:27.470 --> 11:30.160
Be careful. Slow down. Slow down.

11:30.550 --> 11:31.470
Be careful.

11:34.190 --> 11:36.190
Very good. Slow down.

11:37.310 --> 11:38.520
Slow down.

11:56.040 --> 11:56.970
All these years,

11:58.500 --> 12:00.160
I thought silence and absence

12:00.670 --> 12:02.470
were protection and sacrifice.

12:03.440 --> 12:04.760
But year after year,

12:05.590 --> 12:06.710
day after day,

12:07.950 --> 12:09.670
in every day of my absence,

12:10.160 --> 12:11.490
you stubbornly waited.

12:12.950 --> 12:13.710
Mu.

12:14.920 --> 12:17.120
Thank you for staying with me all along,

12:17.520 --> 12:18.780
helping me understand

12:19.750 --> 12:22.480
that true love
isn't self-righteous sacrifice,

12:22.710 --> 12:23.950
but 2 hearts,

12:25.120 --> 12:28.320
defying wind and rain together,
resisting a broken life.

12:31.160 --> 12:32.160
I understand now.

12:33.520 --> 12:34.520
True courage

12:35.040 --> 12:36.970
isn't charging into battle alone.

12:37.750 --> 12:39.030
It's allowing oneself

12:39.840 --> 12:42.240
to become a wound that's tenderly guarded.

12:49.530 --> 12:50.180
Try this.

13:02.470 --> 13:03.400
It's delicious.

13:20.120 --> 13:21.650
Is there any difference...

13:22.880 --> 13:23.880
from what he made?

13:39.370 --> 13:40.160
At that time,

13:40.920 --> 13:41.980
I was still abroad.

13:43.040 --> 13:45.040
The rehabilitation was going well.

13:45.470 --> 13:47.050
I no longer needed a wheelchair

13:47.050 --> 13:48.450
and could manage to walk.

13:49.790 --> 13:51.070
Lin Sui kept asking me

13:51.310 --> 13:52.970
to be his driver in the future.

13:53.470 --> 13:55.000
I understood what he meant.

13:56.400 --> 13:58.260
He was encouraging me in that way.

13:59.240 --> 14:01.310
Given my physical condition at the time,

14:01.310 --> 14:02.840
how could I possibly drive?

14:04.730 --> 14:07.260
And I didn't know
what I could do in the future.

14:07.600 --> 14:08.910
I wondered what you

14:10.550 --> 14:11.790
would want me to do.

14:14.190 --> 14:15.990
You'd probably want me to study.

14:17.190 --> 14:18.920
When I got tired from studying,

14:20.040 --> 14:22.240
I would read the letters you wrote to me.

14:23.240 --> 14:24.120
Those letters

14:24.790 --> 14:25.790
gave me faith.

14:57.250 --> 14:58.890
Kid, come and eat!

15:33.760 --> 15:35.000
Noodles are here.

15:36.090 --> 15:36.820
Chopsticks.

15:40.240 --> 15:40.950
Wait.

15:42.520 --> 15:43.580
Chopped scallions

15:43.830 --> 15:45.830
are the soul of this bowl of noodles.

15:55.640 --> 15:57.280
How's your studying going?

15:58.130 --> 15:58.730
Not bad.

15:59.240 --> 16:00.360
Don't overwork yourself.

16:00.360 --> 16:02.310
Your body needs more rest now.

16:22.670 --> 16:24.730
Have you been in touch with Mu lately?

16:27.310 --> 16:28.370
When Mu was little,

16:29.230 --> 16:31.830
she loved it most
when I cooked noodles for her.

16:34.830 --> 16:36.240
When you get the chance in the future,

16:36.240 --> 16:38.240
help me cook a bowl of noodles for Mu.

16:40.160 --> 16:41.000
I hope

16:41.360 --> 16:44.160
she can remember the taste
of this bowl of noodles.

17:00.950 --> 17:01.640
Got it.

17:07.530 --> 17:08.660
I've quit drinking.

17:10.430 --> 17:11.560
I've quit drinking.

17:13.329 --> 17:13.890
Why?

17:14.079 --> 17:15.510
I can't handle it anymore.

17:15.510 --> 17:16.119
I'm tired.

17:22.700 --> 17:25.300
I need to take good care
of your sister, Jin Xin.

17:26.990 --> 17:28.030
I can't

17:28.470 --> 17:30.070
make the same mistake again.

17:46.700 --> 17:47.310
Eat.

17:50.080 --> 17:50.880
How does it taste?

17:50.880 --> 17:51.610
Pretty good.

17:51.750 --> 17:52.800
Good. Eat more.

18:02.160 --> 18:03.760
Maybe it's because he's old.

18:06.120 --> 18:07.320
He's a bit...

18:08.510 --> 18:09.510
sentimental now.

18:15.990 --> 18:18.510
He's realized that he wasn't there for you

18:18.880 --> 18:21.340
during some important moments
in your life.

18:22.950 --> 18:23.950
And he regrets it.

18:28.560 --> 18:30.080
He wants to make it up to you,

18:30.080 --> 18:32.280
even if it's just cooking you a good meal

18:33.640 --> 18:35.300
or a bowl of Yangchun noodles.

18:37.950 --> 18:39.030
He wants you to know

18:39.560 --> 18:40.890
that his love for you...

18:42.430 --> 18:43.320
isn't fake.

18:45.430 --> 18:47.120
He just lost himself before.

18:50.160 --> 18:51.270
Actually,

18:52.800 --> 18:54.880
he could have told me all this
over the phone.

18:54.880 --> 18:56.280
I understand him on this.

19:00.750 --> 19:02.190
Men sometimes

19:04.600 --> 19:07.000
aren't very good at saying mushy things...

19:11.160 --> 19:12.190
face to face.

19:20.560 --> 19:22.420
I stopped resenting him long ago.

19:25.160 --> 19:26.270
I only remember...

19:27.780 --> 19:29.130
that he loved racing.

19:29.640 --> 19:30.880
When I was little,

19:32.030 --> 19:34.670
he always took me out to play with cars
behind Mom's back.

19:34.670 --> 19:35.640
Without cars,

19:36.160 --> 19:37.690
it was like he lost his soul.

19:41.990 --> 19:43.120
I won't be like that.

19:45.800 --> 19:46.670
Racing...

19:48.360 --> 19:49.400
isn't my dream.

19:53.080 --> 19:54.560
Then what is your dream?

20:00.320 --> 20:01.230
My dream...

20:03.430 --> 20:05.030
is for you to always be happy.

20:06.370 --> 20:09.520
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

20:09.830 --> 20:12.770
♪ You, weaving through my heart ♪

20:11.190 --> 20:12.160
Me too.

20:13.240 --> 20:17.030
♪ My thoughts of you will never cease ♪

20:17.050 --> 20:21.740
♪ Waiting for your ship to arrive ♪

20:21.850 --> 20:24.530
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

20:22.430 --> 20:23.190
From now on,

20:24.400 --> 20:25.560
no matter what you do,

20:24.920 --> 20:28.370
♪ You, chasing after the moon ♪

20:26.430 --> 20:27.830
I'll always support you.

20:28.930 --> 20:31.200
♪ Scattered across the sky ♪

20:31.280 --> 20:34.960
♪ And me, here by your side ♪

20:35.990 --> 20:36.670
Mu.

20:41.600 --> 20:42.430
I want us...

20:51.510 --> 20:53.430
to go to Canada together next month.

20:52.980 --> 20:55.880
♪ Stars are twinkling in the sky ♪

20:55.880 --> 20:57.400
Let's visit...

20:56.270 --> 20:59.240
♪ Like your twinkling eyes ♪

20:59.490 --> 21:02.260
♪ Telling me ♪

21:03.510 --> 21:06.090
♪ A beautiful dream from afar ♪

21:06.120 --> 21:06.800
Mom.

21:08.150 --> 21:11.370
♪ Night is painted with neon lights ♪

21:09.920 --> 21:10.840
Can you do it?

21:11.880 --> 21:14.960
♪ The softly bustling street ♪

21:15.190 --> 21:19.030
♪ I paused and wandered far ♪

21:19.420 --> 21:23.070
♪ You're like a breeze ♪

21:23.860 --> 21:26.380
♪ I watch you leave ♪

21:27.190 --> 21:30.630
♪ I wish I could hug you from the back ♪

21:31.090 --> 21:34.160
♪ Lingering in the air ♪

21:34.470 --> 21:37.630
♪ Your breath is everywhere ♪

21:39.120 --> 21:42.270
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

21:42.580 --> 21:45.520
♪ You, weaving through my heart ♪

21:45.990 --> 21:49.770
♪ My thoughts of you will never cease ♪

21:49.800 --> 21:54.490
♪ Waiting for your ship to arrive ♪

21:54.540 --> 21:57.570
♪ I'm still waiting, still waiting ♪

21:57.650 --> 22:01.100
♪ You, chasing after the moon ♪

22:01.830 --> 22:04.100
♪ Scattered across the sky ♪

22:04.260 --> 22:07.400
♪ And me, here by your side ♪

22:07.820 --> 22:12.020
♪ No matter if it's clear
or rainy tonight ♪

22:16.700 --> 22:24.030
♪ I'll keep the light on for you ♪

22:25.710 --> 22:28.940
♪ Night is painted with neon lights ♪

22:29.140 --> 22:32.220
♪ The softly bustling street ♪

22:32.450 --> 22:36.290
♪ I paused and wandered far ♪

22:36.680 --> 22:40.330
♪ You're like a breeze ♪

22:37.470 --> 22:40.000
When you
wouldn't let Mu contact me back then,

22:41.120 --> 22:43.640
♪ I watch you leave ♪

22:41.160 --> 22:43.690
had you already seen the weakness
in my heart?

22:44.450 --> 22:47.890
♪ I wish I could hug you from the back ♪

22:45.430 --> 22:47.560
And now I'm coming to visit you with it.

22:48.350 --> 22:51.420
♪ Lingering in the air ♪

22:50.160 --> 22:51.620
Actually, what I fear most

22:51.730 --> 22:54.890
♪ Your breath is everywhere ♪

22:52.400 --> 22:53.800
is not your disapproval,

22:54.750 --> 22:56.480
but your sadness and disappointment.

22:56.480 --> 22:59.630
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

22:58.120 --> 22:59.920
After all, the one taking Mu away

22:59.940 --> 23:02.880
♪ You, weaving through my heart ♪

23:00.560 --> 23:02.690
is me, the person you least want to see.

23:03.350 --> 23:07.140
♪ My thoughts of you will never cease ♪

23:03.510 --> 23:05.240
But Mu has taught me to be brave.

23:06.510 --> 23:07.600
So this time,

23:07.160 --> 23:11.850
♪ Waiting for your ship to arrive ♪

23:08.600 --> 23:10.800
please allow me to lay the rest of my life

23:11.160 --> 23:12.400
before you.

23:11.960 --> 23:14.640
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

23:15.030 --> 23:18.480
♪ You, chasing after the moon ♪

23:19.040 --> 23:21.310
♪ Scattered across the sky ♪

23:21.230 --> 23:21.920
Young man,

23:21.390 --> 23:25.070
♪ And me, here by your side ♪

23:22.710 --> 23:24.570
could you help take a photo for us?

23:25.090 --> 23:30.210
♪ This heart that wanders with you ♪

23:25.360 --> 23:25.920
Sure.

23:26.470 --> 23:27.270
Thank you.

23:30.320 --> 23:30.990
Thank you.

23:30.480 --> 23:34.070
♪ Only wishes you'd smile ♪

23:34.300 --> 23:38.280
♪ All the withered grass on earth ♪

23:38.400 --> 23:43.170
♪ Has bloomed for you ♪

23:45.950 --> 23:46.470
Done.

23:46.710 --> 23:47.410
Take a look.

23:47.040 --> 23:50.190
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

23:49.270 --> 23:50.500
-So lovely.
-Really nice.

23:50.500 --> 23:53.440
♪ You, weaving through my heart ♪

23:50.750 --> 23:51.430
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

23:51.430 --> 23:52.270
Thank you.

23:52.400 --> 23:53.910
Alright, let's go over there.

23:53.910 --> 23:57.700
♪ My thoughts of you will never cease ♪

23:53.920 --> 23:54.640
Thank you.

23:57.720 --> 24:02.410
♪ Waiting for your ship to arrive ♪

24:02.520 --> 24:05.200
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

24:05.590 --> 24:09.040
♪ You, chasing after the moon ♪

24:09.600 --> 24:11.870
♪ Scattered across the sky ♪

24:11.950 --> 24:15.630
♪ And me, here by your side ♪

24:15.670 --> 24:19.870
♪ No matter if it's clear
or rainy tonight ♪

24:24.380 --> 24:31.710
♪ I'll keep the light on for you ♪

25:14.190 --> 25:15.450
When we get home later,

25:16.430 --> 25:18.470
if Mom says anything unpleasant,

25:19.320 --> 25:20.600
don't take it to heart.

25:25.750 --> 25:27.680
If I'm afraid to face these things,

25:28.100 --> 25:29.300
I wouldn't have come.

25:36.270 --> 25:38.080
If you hadn't come back to me,

25:39.230 --> 25:40.190
I don't know

25:41.270 --> 25:42.160
if I would ever have had the chance

25:42.160 --> 25:44.020
to see her again in this lifetime.

26:23.130 --> 26:24.810
Mu, welcome home.

26:25.320 --> 26:26.400
I just said it was you two,

26:26.400 --> 26:28.130
but your mom didn't believe me.

26:29.320 --> 26:31.120
Chris, let me introduce him to you.

26:31.120 --> 26:32.070
He is Jin Zhao.

26:35.030 --> 26:35.710
Welcome.

26:36.710 --> 26:37.510
Hello, Uncle.

26:39.470 --> 26:41.470
You look quite spirited, young man.

26:45.600 --> 26:47.000
Come on, let's go inside.

27:57.670 --> 27:58.400
Honey.

28:00.400 --> 28:01.320
Mu is here.

28:01.960 --> 28:02.620
She's here?

28:02.640 --> 28:03.770
Jin Zhao is here too.

28:06.340 --> 28:07.010
Got it.

28:24.280 --> 28:25.760
Mom, I'm back.

28:26.650 --> 28:27.450
You're back.

28:28.650 --> 28:29.450
Are you tired?

28:30.030 --> 28:31.020
I told you

28:31.120 --> 28:32.260
to send me a message,

28:32.510 --> 28:34.360
so I could ask Chris
to pick you up at the airport.

28:34.360 --> 28:36.670
No need to trouble him. We took a taxi.

28:38.120 --> 28:38.770
Mom,

28:39.320 --> 28:40.510
Zhao is back too.

28:50.880 --> 28:51.470
Look,

28:51.750 --> 28:52.640
I'm preparing

28:52.640 --> 28:53.920
dinner for tonight.

28:54.200 --> 28:56.600
Take your luggage to the room
and rest a bit.

28:57.230 --> 28:58.690
Dinner will be ready soon.

29:17.510 --> 29:18.160
Here, Mu,

29:18.190 --> 29:19.250
have some shrimps.

29:19.800 --> 29:21.080
Mu, you know what?

29:21.410 --> 29:22.880
Chris is worried and curious

29:22.880 --> 29:24.160
about your work.

29:24.560 --> 29:25.400
Worried?

29:25.920 --> 29:27.050
Worried about what?

29:27.320 --> 29:28.880
In your last call,

29:29.190 --> 29:30.880
you said the sun was going to explode

29:30.880 --> 29:32.280
and we'd all turn to dust.

29:32.310 --> 29:34.360
He was so scared
that he couldn't sleep well for a week.

29:34.360 --> 29:35.320
Right?

29:37.270 --> 29:39.670
That was just an astrophysics documentary.

29:39.670 --> 29:41.640
Before that, there is another line:

29:41.640 --> 29:43.570
"It will take about 6 billion years

29:43.710 --> 29:45.440
before the sun might explode."

29:45.510 --> 29:47.120
The life cycle of celestial bodies

29:47.120 --> 29:49.180
is closely related to life and death.

29:49.430 --> 29:50.430
Think about it.

29:50.800 --> 29:52.920
If there's an atom in your body

29:53.220 --> 29:55.230
that was once born, grew, and decayed

29:55.230 --> 29:57.670
in the distant cosmos,

29:58.190 --> 29:59.720
how romantic would that be?

30:00.470 --> 30:02.710
It does sound romantic.

30:03.470 --> 30:05.800
But why did I find it terrifying
last time?

30:05.840 --> 30:06.950
It's not terrifying.

30:06.950 --> 30:08.750
It's that you're a scaredy-cat.

30:08.880 --> 30:10.190
If Earth is going to explode,

30:10.190 --> 30:11.850
shouldn't we be a bit nervous?

30:11.990 --> 30:12.640
Honey,

30:12.990 --> 30:15.050
I think you've always been very calm.

30:15.400 --> 30:18.400
You must have known
it'll take 6 billion years, right?

30:18.470 --> 30:19.400
Yes, yes.

30:19.830 --> 30:21.270
After Mu mentioned it last time,

30:21.270 --> 30:23.350
I immediately watched that documentary.

30:23.350 --> 30:24.750
I even watched it 3 times.

30:24.920 --> 30:27.720
Actually,
you were just worrying unnecessarily.

30:27.950 --> 30:28.950
Stupid.

30:29.950 --> 30:31.320
What? Annoying?

30:31.880 --> 30:33.360
Well, Honey,

30:34.120 --> 30:35.560
did I upset you again?

30:39.750 --> 30:40.400
Zhao,

30:40.840 --> 30:42.770
you watched that documentary too.

30:42.990 --> 30:44.030
Cosmic Wonders.

30:46.190 --> 30:47.600
There's a red nebula in it.

30:47.600 --> 30:49.400
The visuals are very beautiful.

30:49.750 --> 30:50.710
Such a big dumpling—

30:50.710 --> 30:52.240
I bet it can shut your mouth.

30:59.920 --> 31:01.180
You've all watched it?

31:01.230 --> 31:02.320
So I've been alone?

31:03.080 --> 31:04.360
You mean "isolated", right?

31:04.360 --> 31:05.270
Not "alone".

31:07.540 --> 31:08.210
Fine.

31:14.560 --> 31:15.160
Mu,

31:15.470 --> 31:16.930
how's your current place?

31:24.560 --> 31:25.890
I terminated the lease.

31:26.270 --> 31:26.920
What?

31:27.360 --> 31:28.820
You terminated the lease?

31:29.640 --> 31:30.840
Where do you live now?

31:39.800 --> 31:41.400
Mu is staying at my place now.

32:08.880 --> 32:10.430
I don't think it'll take

32:10.820 --> 32:12.880
6 billion years for Earth to explode.

32:13.190 --> 32:14.470
Mu, don't you think so?

32:18.950 --> 32:19.510
Also,

32:19.620 --> 32:21.310
next time you watch a movie,

32:21.330 --> 32:22.590
take me with you, okay?

32:47.360 --> 32:48.890
Jin Zhao,
this is your first time in Canada,

32:48.890 --> 32:49.290
right?

32:49.360 --> 32:50.160
Yes, Uncle.

32:51.270 --> 32:53.600
Since you're here, make yourself at home.

32:53.670 --> 32:54.400
Relax.

32:55.120 --> 32:56.880
In the morning, you can get up early.

32:56.880 --> 32:58.190
The air is especially fresh.

32:58.190 --> 32:59.320
You might see some small animals,

32:59.320 --> 33:01.230
like beavers and red foxes.

33:01.430 --> 33:03.470
-They are not afraid of humans.
-Chris.

33:03.470 --> 33:04.920
I told you to help me tidy the guest room.

33:04.920 --> 33:05.950
Is it ready?

33:09.670 --> 33:10.470
It's ready.

33:10.640 --> 33:11.190
Okay.

34:01.240 --> 34:01.920
Jin Zhao,

34:02.950 --> 34:03.990
you're still up?

34:24.429 --> 34:26.489
I don't have any elders around to ask,

34:28.429 --> 34:30.880
so I asked my colleagues
about the customs...

34:30.880 --> 34:32.280
for proposing marriage.

34:37.830 --> 34:41.489
I'm not sure if I've missed anything
or done anything improperly.

35:18.550 --> 35:19.840
I'm not someone

35:19.840 --> 35:21.970
who can fully meet your expectations,

35:22.840 --> 35:24.040
but Mu has always been

35:25.160 --> 35:27.240
the person I cherish most,

35:28.660 --> 35:30.790
whether as a younger sister in the past

35:32.390 --> 35:34.320
or as a beloved partner from now on.

35:43.360 --> 35:44.360
I came this time

35:45.720 --> 35:47.150
to tell you in person...

35:48.990 --> 35:50.110
that from now on,

35:51.240 --> 35:53.300
no matter what circumstances I face,

35:55.330 --> 35:57.130
I will take good care of Mu

35:58.290 --> 36:00.170
and never let her suffer.

36:08.130 --> 36:09.130
Please...

36:11.380 --> 36:12.420
entrust her to me.

37:05.320 --> 37:06.110
Mom.

37:55.000 --> 37:56.800
You two had a long journey today.

37:57.730 --> 37:58.770
Rest early.

38:19.840 --> 38:20.510
Jin Zhao,

38:21.720 --> 38:23.320
some things can't be rushed.

38:23.580 --> 38:24.380
Take it slow.

38:26.680 --> 38:27.880
And give her some time.
